SELECT 
    DWH_APPS_ID, 
    APPS_NAME,
    DWH_TYPE, 
    DWH_INSTANCE, 
    DWH_TARGET, 
    DWH_SEQ, 
    DWH_SOURCE, 
    DWH_SCHEMA, 
    DWH_MODE,
    DWH_DAYS, 
    DWH_DT_UPDATE, 
    DWH_STATUS, 
    DWH_AUDIT_USER, 
    DWH_AUDIT_DATE, 
    DWH_DT_CTRL, 
    DWH_CTRL_STATUS, 
    DWH_BEFORE, 
    DWH_AFTER, 
    DWH_GROUP, 
    DWH_PK, 
    DWH_DELTA,
    DWH_QUERY, 
    DWH_CTRL_WHERE
FROM 
    SETTINGS_DWH
INNER JOIN
    SETTINGS_APPLICATIONS 
    ON APPS_ID = DWH_APPS_ID

SELECT
  DWH_APPS_ID,
  DWH_TYPE,
  DWH_INSTANCE,
  DWH_TARGET,
  DBMS_LOB.substr(DWH_LOG) DWH_LOG
FROM
 SETTINGS_DWH
